TI  - Debris-flow susceptibility assessment at regional scale: Validation on an alpine environment
T2  - LANDSLIDES
LA  - English
KW  - Debris flow
KW  - Susceptibility assessment
KW  - Physical models
KW  - Statistical model
KW  - Pyrenees
KW  - PHYSICALLY-BASED MODEL
