TI  - Unusual disturbance: forest change following a catastrophic debris flow in the Canadian Rocky Mountains
T2  - CANADIAN JOURNAL OF FOREST RESEARCH-REVUE CANADIENNE DE RECHERCHE FORESTIERE
LA  - English
KW  - COTTONWOOD SEEDLING RECRUITMENT
