TI  - A long lacustrine record from the Pianico-Sellere Basin (Middle-Late Pleistocene, Northern Italy)
T2  - QUATERNARY INTERNATIONAL
LA  - English
KW  - VEGETATION CHANGE
KW  - LAKE GENEVA
