TI  - Spatial and temporal evolution of co-seismic landslides after the 2005 Kashmir earthquake
T2  - GEOMORPHOLOGY
LA  - English
KW  - 2005 Kashmir earthquake
KW  - Co-seismic landslides
KW  - Temporal dynamics
KW  - Spatial and temporal analysis
KW  - SPOT
KW  - RAINFALL-INDUCED LANDSLIDES
KW  - CHI-CHI-EARTHQUAKE
KW  - WENCHUAN EARTHQUAKE
KW  - DEBRIS FLOW
