TI  - PALAEODEPOSITIONAL CONTEXT OF A CAMBRIAN AEOLIAN SYSTEM: PEDRA PINTADA AND PEDRA DAS TORRINHAS FORMATIONS (CAMAQUA BASIN, BRAZIL)
T2  - BOLETIM PARANAENSE DE GEOCIENCIAS
LA  - Portuguese
KW  - eolian dunes
