TI  - Facies and depositional model of alluvial fan dominated by episodic flood events in arid conditions: An example from the Quaternary Poplar Fan, north-western China
T2  - SEDIMENTOLOGY
LA  - English
KW  - Alluvial fan
KW  - arid conditions
KW  - depositional model
